parameters.name: DOY
parameters.description:
Quantity: Day of year of the observation, days
              are counted from 1 on

parameters.name: Decyear
parameters.description:
Quantity: Fractional year of the observation. Includes the
              full time information in one number. When converting
              to day of year, ensure that round years
              (like 1995.00) have to be equal to DOY
              1, not DOY 0.

parameters.name: Step
parameters.description:
Quantity: This is technical information added for completeness.
              For HGA_Flag=1, "step" shows the actual motor positions
              0-7. For HGA_Flag=0 this information is not available
              and the value set to invalid (-1E38).

parameters.name: Spin
parameters.description:
Quantity: This is technical information added for completeness.
              For HGA_Flag=1, "spin" is the number of sectors
              in the sky. Its range is 0-63. For
              HGA_Flag=0, this information is not available and the
              value set to invalid (-1E38).

parameters.name: Ej_keV
parameters.description:
Quantity: Deposited energy in CMS/DeltaExE solid state detector
              Ja or Jb, depending on the used telescope
              indicated by "detector". This energy is lower than
              the ambient energy of the particle due to
              the pulse height defect and because the energy
              was reduced in the SSD dead layer.

parameters.name: Ek_keV
parameters.description:
Quantity: Deposited energy in CMS/DeltaExE solid state detector
              Ka or Kb, depending on the used telescope
              indicated by "detector". This energy is lower than
              the ambient energy of the particle due to
              the pulse height defect and because the energy
              was reduced when the particle passed the J.
              Comparison of Ej_keV and Ek_keV allows to identify
              ion species.

parameters.name: etcode
parameters.description: Quantity:  This is technical information added for completeness.

parameters.name: detector
parameters.description:
Quantity: This is technical information added for completeness.
              It lists the CMS subsystem: 0 for TOFxE
              end, 1 for Jb/Kb and 3 for Ja/Kb
              of the two DeltaExE ends.

parameters.name: hga_flag
parameters.description:
Quantity: This is technical information added for completeness.
              Is 1 if the data originates from record
              mode, 0 if the data is from real
              time mode.
